OL,3,CBBC confirms satellite SD switch-off
OL,4,Cdate
OL,6,GThe BBC has confirmed it will be
OL,7,Gclosing its standard definition TV
OL,8,Gservices via satellite on Monday 8th
OL,9,GJanuary 2024.
OL,11,FOn-screen messaging now advises
OL,12,Faffected satellite users to take
OL,13,Faction and upgrade to an HD-
OL,14,Fcompatible satellite receiver. Sky is
OL,15,Foffering its customers a free upgrade
OL,16,Fto a newer receiver.
OL,18,FSimulcasts of BBC channels in
OL,19,Fstandard definition above channel 800
OL,20,Fon the Sky satellite EPG will also
OL,21,Fcease at this point.
