OL,3,CBBC confirms satellite SD switch-off
OL,4,Cdate
OL,6,FNotably, radio stations will also be
OL,7,Faffected. The BBC is in the process
OL,8,Fof moving them to sit alongside the
OL,9,Fexisting HD channels on satellite
OL,10,Ftransponders running in DVB-S2 mode.
OL,11,FThat means older satellite receivers,
OL,12,Fbuilt to receive DVB-S(1) services
OL,13,Fwill no longer be able to receive BBC
OL,14,Fradio via satellite.
OL,16,FThe closedown is the culmination of a
OL,17,Fyear-long project that has seen the
OL,18,FBBC launch HD versions of each
OL,19,Fchannel on satellite after a wait of
OL,20,Fover a decade.
