OL,3,CBBC confirms satellite SD switch-off
OL,4,Cdate
OL,6,FBack in November last year, Kieran
OL,7,FClifton, BBC Director of Distribution
OL,8,Fand Business Development indicated
OL,9,Fthe switch-off would happen by the
OL,10,Fend of March. However, this has now
OL,11,Fbeen brought forward, with relatively
OL,12,Ffew households contacting the BBC for
OL,13,Fhelp migrating.
OL,15,FSeparately, the BBC plans to close
OL,16,FBBC Radio 4 LW at the end of March,
OL,17,Fcoinciding with the end of a contract
OL,18,Fto provide the teleswitching service
OL,19,Ffor Economy 7 meters.
